{"tid":2210333,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英衛生大臣指處於疫情臨界點　不排除第二次全國封城","createTime":"2020-09-20T10:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T11:39:46.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f220c959ba94c83bd86366c1acc12ad69b7cfeb6","tid":2210333,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T10:27:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550664-20200920.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550664-20200920.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=eCiXx0TsV7ZnsYjNRM2Omh%2FwB%2Fd2Hr%2Bf%2F5fgrRWXORU%3D&h=09de40d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1550664-20200920.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=b229d817\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1550664-20200920.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國衛生大臣夏國賢說，官員星期日開會商討倫敦需要甚麼抗疫封鎖措施。<br />\n<br />\n夏國賢形容，英國處於新型肺炎疫情的臨界點，警告假如民眾不遵守政府的抗疫規例，他不能排除作出第二次全國「封城」的決定。<br />\n<br />\n英國最近幾個星期疫情反彈，單日新增確診個案超過4000宗，首相約翰遜形容為第二波疫情，早前說計劃在全國範圍，實施更嚴厲的封鎖措施。<br />\n<br />\n另外，俄羅斯星期日新增超過6100宗病例，連續第2日宗數在6000以上，全國累積約110萬人確診。"},{"pid":"4aa396fb7793e76762d3006a60fb21630c00da7c","tid":2210333,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"英國經濟冇可能頂到第二次lockdown <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ebf926942961cae9481a6d05b5149e3985808a0","tid":2210333,"uid":11703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:18:13.000Z","msg":"冇可能喇"},{"pid":"50d156467a6f5813bda61e3d30d8ecd839e59047","tid":2210333,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4aa396fb7793e76762d3006a60fb21630c00da7c","tid":2210333,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-20T11:06:31.000Z","msg":"英國經濟冇可能頂到第二次lockdown <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /